# Walkthrough: Seed Curriculum & Fix Course Display

## What Was Done

### 1. Extended [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#62-82) Schema
[Academic.ts](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts) — Added optional `curriculum` embedded sub-document with typed sub-schemas:
- `CurriculumUnitSubSchema`, `CurriculumSemesterSubSchema`, `CurriculumProcedureSubSchema`, `CurriculumScenarioSubSchema`
- `CurriculumSubSchema` — overview, academic_structure, detailed_syllabus, practical_procedures, case_scenarios, internship, assessment, career_pathways, student_engagement
- All fields default to `undefined` — **zero impact on existing records**

### 2. Created Seed Script
[seed_curriculum.js](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/scripts/seed_curriculum.js) — Reads `ai_output/diploma/*.json` and upserts curriculum data into matching [Program](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/Academic.ts#62-82) records.
- **Code Alias Map**: Handles 3 mismatched codes (DCP→DCCP, DHCP→DIHCP, DHSI→DSHI)
- Also backfills `description`, `syllabus[]`, and `careerOptions[]` if they were sparse
- Does NOT delete any data

### 3. Updated Course Detail API
[page.tsx (server)](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/courses/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx) — [toClientCourse()](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/courses/%5Bid%5D/page.tsx#25-44) now accepts `includeCurriculum` flag and passes the full curriculum object to the client on detail pages.

### 4. Rewrote Frontend Detail Page
[CourseDetailClient.tsx](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28public%29/courses/%5Bid%5D/CourseDetailClient.tsx) — Dynamic section rendering with graceful fallbacks:

| Section | Source | Fallback |
|---|---|---|
| Program Overview | `curriculum.overview` | Basic `description` |
| Academic Structure | `curriculum.academic_structure` | Hidden |
| Detailed Syllabus | `curriculum.detailed_syllabus` (accordions) | Basic `syllabus[]` list |
| Practical Training | `curriculum.practical_procedures` | Hidden |
| Case Scenarios | `curriculum.case_scenarios` | Hidden |
| Internship | `curriculum.internship` | Hidden |
| Assessment | `curriculum.assessment` | Hidden |
| Career Pathways | `curriculum.career_pathways` | Basic `career[]` tags |
| Student Engagement | `curriculum.student_engagement` | Hidden |

